like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:53:43.000Z","msg":"大陸而家真係出口同內需都贏哂<br />\n出口野依然夠平, 內部消費又恢復得最快<br />\n一個疫情事實係玩殘咗歐美, 佢地自己亦真係控制得好好<br />\n我諗無謂再FF大陸仲有好多隱形傳播, 爆到七彩等等打飛機野"},{"pid":"01b53bafa75e156918554f46a8aa5a292bf180e1","tid":2240974,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"穏中向好、長期向好嘅基本面冇改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓喺度都贏"},{"pid":"1a34d9cbd30869a3fc0745ba6c6a369acbbc9a52","tid":2240974,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9a9699657c39bfdfd476b5c926b09d2eae63192","tid":2240974,"uid":362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf13295fc3c13de3efa3074630c1d584a7a09077","tid":2240974,"uid":168564,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"通常中國呢啲咁嘅數據，係有水份喺度<br />\n睇中國嘅數字唔需要太認真，一般將中共嘅數據打返個六折左右就差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"如果長期都係六折，咁都係有增長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:59:18.000Z","msg":"都係新高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02361458f0b9034e25c34149d7c61985e40f7f8b","tid":2240974,"uid":357710,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e01d74f5701d104a744993d9db90b828c606608","tid":2240974,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fef98c30c8c2148f81bb069472bfb9f06c1ed18","tid":2240974,"uid":357710,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf13295fc3c13de3efa3074630c1d584a7a09077","tid":2240974,"uid":168564,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"通常中國呢啲咁嘅數據，係有水份喺度<br />\n睇中國嘅數字唔需要太認真，一般將中共嘅數據打返個六折左右就差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-1